{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01G7BRp3rDFXYdVexnK5T3C5","type":"tool_result","content":"   530→**3d-vii: Failure handling — code bugs vs infrastructure failures**\n   531→\n   532→Determine the failure type. There are two distinct paths:\n   533→\n   534→**Path A — Code bugs (`pending > 0` in proof validation):**\n   535→\n   536→A proof document exists and `codeharness verify` reported `pending > 0`. This means the feature has real bugs — the code does not satisfy the ACs. Code bugs NEVER count against the retry budget.\n   537→\n   538→1. **Extract failing ACs from the proof document.** Read `verification/{story_key}-proof.md`. For each AC section (`## AC N: description`), check if the verdict is not PASS and not `[ESCALATE]`. For each failing AC, extract:\n   539→   - The AC number and description (from the `## AC N:` heading)\n   540→   - The error output (from the `output` code blocks and any verdict text)\n   541→\n   542→2. **Save findings to the story file.** Read `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/{story_key}.md`. If it already has a `## Verification Findings` section, replace that section entirely with the new findings. If not, append a new `## Verification Findings` section before the `## Dev Agent Record` section (or at the end if that section doesn't exist). Format:\n   543→   ```markdown\n   544→   ## Verification Findings\n   545→\n   546→   _Last updated: {timestamp}_\n   547→\n   548→   The following ACs failed black-box verification:\n   549→\n   550→   ### AC {N}: {description}\n   551→   **Verdict:** FAIL\n   552→   **Error output:**\n   553→   ```\n   554→   {relevant error output from proof}\n   555→   ```\n   556→\n   557→   {repeat for each failing AC}\n   558→   ```\n   559→\n   560→3. **Increment `attempts`.** If `attempts >= max_attempts` (10):\n   561→   - Increment `stories_skipped`\n   562→   - Append `{story_key}: verify↔dev cycle limit (10)` to `skipped_reasons`\n   563→   - Print: `[WARN] Story {story_key}: verify↔dev cycle limit reached — skipping`\n   564→   - Run cleanup (step 3d-viii)\n   565→   - Go to Step 2 (next story)\n   566→\n   567→4. **Return story to dev.** Update sprint-status.yaml: change `{story_key}` status from `verifying` to `in-progress`.\n   568→\n   569→5. **Reset retry count.** Update `ralph/.story_retries`: write/replace the line `{story_key}=0` in the file (read existing file first to preserve other entries). This resets the infra retry budget since the story is going back to dev.\n   570→\n   571→6. Print: `[WARN] Story {story_key}: verification found {N} failing ACs — returning to dev (attempt {attempts}/{max_attempts})`\n   572→\n   573→7. Run cleanup (step 3d-viii).\n   574→\n   575→8. Go to Step 3b (dev-story) — the story is now `in-progress` and the dev prompt will include the verification findings.\n   576→\n   577→**Path B — Infrastructure failures (timeout, docker error, no proof produced, verifier non-zero exit WITHOUT a proof):**\n   578→\n   579→The verification could not complete due to infrastructure issues — NOT code quality."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01PmuW6xAsA3LVJUCbfjE8R9","session_id":"caf97759-8abf-4687-a81a-d927d13354ea","uuid":"5e03b3b1-46ee-45c1-accd-1b19e291a01e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T12:57:49.717Z"}
